Intern Manager Web Application(DecodeLabs Project 4)

Project Description

This is a full stack web application developed using Flask, SQLite, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
The application allows users to manage intern details with basic CRUD operations (Create, Read, Delete).

---

✨ Features

- ➕ Add new interns
- 📋 View all interns
- ❌ Delete interns
- 💾 Data stored in SQLite database
- 🔗 Frontend connected with Flask backend API

---

Technologies Used

- Python (Flask)
- SQLite Database
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Flask-CORS

---

